                            <td><strong>Created</strong></td>
                            <td>Mar 22, 2025</td>
                            <td>Mar 18, 2025</td>
                            <td>Mar 15, 2025</td>
                            <td>Mar 20, 2025</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <div class="match-reasons">
                    <strong><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Algorithm Analysis (Hashed Data Only):</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Name hash match:</strong> 95-98% similarity detected across 3 records</li>
                        <li><strong>DOB hash match:</strong> Exact match on 2 records, 1-day variance on third</li>
                        <li><strong>SSN hashes:</strong> Partial match detected on 2 records</li>
                        <li><strong>Estimated confidence:</strong> 85-92 points (high probability same person)</li>
                        <li style="margin-top: 12px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--orange);">
                            <strong style="color: var(--orange);"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Cannot confirm match without PII access.</strong> Contact Street Outreach Team administrator to enable data sharing for network participants.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" style="flex: 1; background: var(--orange); border-color: var(--orange);">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Request Consent from Org
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn" style="flex: 1;" onclick="closeConsentModal()">
                        Cancel
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
